      "output": "{\n  \"search_id\": \"search_079da935dd1b4aeeacd5a8d8a95efafa\",\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx\",\n      \"title\": \"HP Omen 15-ax243dx Repair Help: Learn How to Fix It Yourself.\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx\\n\\nTable of Contents\\n\\n* Background\\n* Identification\\n* Additional Information\\n\\n* Edit\\n* Options\\n\\n* History\\n* \\n* Show Other Languages\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx Repairability: **7** / 10\\n\\nRepairability: **7** / 10\\n\\n# HP Omen 15-ax243dx Repair\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15-ax243dx is a light weight gaming notebook released in 2016.\\n\\nAuthor: vangnam (and 7 other contributors)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\nI Have This\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Spilled sugary soda on power supply adapter. What do I do?\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Battery discharging rapidly from 70% to 7%\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Looking for where to source a specific component\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx |\\n|2 Answers\\n\\n0 Score |### Why showing something went wrong?\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx |\\n\\n## Documents\\n\\n## [Parts](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx)\\n\\n* [Batteries (1)](https://www.ifixit.\\ncom/Parts/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx/Batteries)\\n\\n* [Case Components (1)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx/Case_Components)\\n\\n* [Keyboards (1)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_Omen_15-ax243dx/Keyboards)\\n\\n## [Tools](https://www.ifixit.com/Tools)\\n\\nThese are some common tools used to work on this device. You might not need every tool for every procedure.\\n\\n## Background\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15 ax243dx is the first generation of the popular gaming laptop series from HP. It was released in 2016. The model number of the laptop is W2N35UA based on the manufacturer number.\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15 ax243dx came stocked with 1 TB of storage, 8 GB of RAM, a 2.8-GHz Intel Core i7-7700HQ processor. The main color of the device is black. The device is only 4.9 lbs which is considered to be a low-weight device compared to other gaming laptops. The screen resolution is 1920 x 1080 with a Diagonal FHD IPS UWVA anti-glare WLED-backlit.\\nHowever, this is not a competitive feature because most of the gaming laptops nowadays have the 4K display. With the Nvidia GeForce GTX 1050/Intel HD Graphics 630 embedded in the system, the HP Omen 15-ax243dx is capable of running smoothly in most of the high-quality video games such as Battlefield 1, Call of Duty World War II.\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15-ax243dx was replaced by the HP Omen X on August 22nd, 2017.\\n\\n## Identification\\n\\nThe HP Omen 15 ax243dx laptop can be identified by the model number printed on the label located on the bottom of the device. If the label has been removed, you can find the model number beneath the battery. For additional help identifying your device, visit the [HP Support page](https://support.hp.com/us-en/document/ish_2039298-1862169-16) .\\n\\n## Additional Information\\n\\n* [OMEN by HP 15-ax243dx Laptop PC Product Specifications](https://support.hp.com/ca-en/document/c05381485)\\n* [HP Omen 15-ax243dx Maintenance and Service guide](http://h10032.www1.hp.\\ncom/ctg/Manual/c04620176)\\n* [Comparasion between HP Omen 15-ax243dx with Lenovo and Mac](https://www.gadgetsnow.com/compare-laptops/HP-Omen-15-ax243dx-W2N35UA-Laptop-Core-i7-7th-Gen8-GB1-TB-128-GB-SSDWindows-104-GB-vs-Lenovo-Ideapad-Y700-80Q000E3IH-Laptop-Core-i7-6th-Gen16-GB1-TB-128-GB-SSDWindows-104-GB)\\n* [HP Omen 15-ax243dx on Amazon](https://www.amazon.com/HP-OMEN-15-6-i7-7700HQ-NVIDIA/dp/B01MTG5JYS?tag=ifixitam-20)\\n* [HP Omen 15-ax243dx Review with Specification](http://laptopmedia.com/review/hp-omen-15-gtx-1050-ti-review-beautiful-lightweight-and-compact-chassis-but-comes-at-a-price-and-a-couple-of-trade-offs/)\\n\\n### Author\\n\\nwith 7 other contributors\\n\\n#### vangnam\\n\\nMember since: 10/19/17\\n\\n599 Reputation\\n\\n4 Guides authored\\n\\nBadges: 14\\n\\n* \\n* \\n* \\n\\n\\\\+11 more badges\\n\\n### Team\\n\\n#### UMass Dartmouth, Team S6-G7, Rockett Fall 2017 Member of UMass Dartmouth, Team S6-G7, Rockett Fall 2017\\n\\nUMASSD-ROCKETT-F17S6G7\\n\\n3 Members\\n\\n7 Guides authored\\n\\n**View Statistics:**\\n\\nPast 24 Hours: 7\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_Omen\",\n      \"title\": \"HP OMEN Series Repair Help: Learn How to Fix It Yourself.\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\nHP OMEN Series\\n\\n* Edit\\n* Options\\n\\n* History\\n* \\n* Show Other Languages\\n\\nHP OMEN Series\\n\\n# HP OMEN Series Repair\\n\\nRepair information for the HP OMEN laptop series.\\n\\nAuthor: Kyle Smith (and 3 other contributors)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\n## 6 Categories\\n\\nNew Page\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series ##### HP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ce198wm ##### HP OMEN 15-ce198wm\\n\\nHP OMEN 16 Series ##### HP OMEN 16 Series\\n\\nHP Omen 16 WD0017CI ##### HP Omen 16 WD0017CI\\n\\nHP OMEN 17 Series ##### HP OMEN 17 Series\\n\\nHP OMEN X Series ##### HP OMEN X Series\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|2 Answers\\n\\n1 Score |### Why won't my hp omen laptop not turn on?\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ax280nd |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n1 Score |### How to enable Advance bios in HP Omen 15 (2020)\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ek0000 Series |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n2 Score |### Keyboard Replacement for OMEN 16\\n\\nHP OMEN 16 Series |\\n|3 Answers\\n\\n0 Score |### 5 longe 3 short Caps lock light IDK? OMEN Laptop - 15-dh1005na\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dh0000 Series |\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.howtogeek.com/ifixit-helping-make-hp-laptops-more-repairable/\",\n      \"title\": \"iFixit Is Helping Make HP Laptops More Repairable\",\n      \"publish_date\": \"2025-05-01\",\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"How-To Geek\\nMenu\\nSign in now\\nMenu\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_OMEN_15_Series\",\n      \"title\": \"HP OMEN 15 Series Help: Learn How to Fix It Yourself.\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\n* Edit\\n* Options\\n\\n* History\\n* \\n* Show Other Languages\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\n# HP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\nRepair guides, manuals, and troubleshooting help for HP OMEN 15 Series. Get everything you need to repair your HP OMEN 15 Series yourself.\\n\\nAuthor: Matt Perona (and one other contributor)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|2 Answers\\n\\n1 Score |### Why won't my hp omen laptop not turn on?\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ax280nd |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n1 Score |### How to enable Advance bios in HP Omen 15 (2020)\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ek0000 Series |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n1 Score |### USB port on one side not working -RESOLVED\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ax280nd |\\n|3 Answers\\n\\n0 Score |### 5 longe 3 short Caps lock light IDK? OMEN Laptop - 15-dh1005na\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dh0000 Series |\\n\\n## [Parts](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series)\\n\\n* [Batteries (7)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series/Batteries)\\n\\n* [Case Components (1)](https://www.ifixit.\\ncom/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series/Case_Components)\\n\\n* [Keyboards (2)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series/Keyboards)\\n\\n* [Ports (1)](https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/HP_OMEN_15_Series/Ports)\\n\\n### Author\\n\\nwith 1 other contributor\\n\\n#### Matt Perona\\n\\nMember since: 10/19/22\\n\\n26,545 Reputation\\n\\n0 Guides authored\\n\\nBadges: 16\\n\\n* \\n* \\n* \\n\\n\\\\+13 more badges\\n\\n### Team\\n\\n#### iFixit Member of iFixit\\n\\nStaff\\n\\n122 Members\\n\\n26,591 Guides authored\\n\\n**View Statistics:**\\n\\nPast 24 Hours: 6\\n\\nPast 7 Days: 82\\n\\nPast 30 Days: 307\\n\\nAll Time: 12,521\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/repairability/laptop-repairability-scores\",\n      \"title\": \"Laptop Repairability Scores | Most Repairable Laptops - iFixit\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"# Laptop Repairability Scores\\n\\nJump to Scores\\n\\n# You have the right to repair the things you own—but how easily can that be done?\\n\\nTo find out, our engineers tear down the latest laptops and score their repairability from zero (unrepairable) to ten (easiest to repair) so you can pick a product that is easy to repair and lasts as long as possible.\\n\\n# What makes a repairable device?\\n\\nIt should be straightforward to disassemble and replace whatever’s broken, using parts and instructions supplied (or endorsed) by the manufacturer. But that’s just to start—repairability means so much more. For full details, see our [repairability scoring explainer](https://www.ifixit.com/News/75533/how-ifixit-scores-repairability) .\\n\\n# Repairability is a moving target\\n\\nWe update our scoring rubric frequently to stay current with new technologies, materials, and design trends.\\nThis means that devices scored in years past might not fare exactly the same if they were re-scored today, but they can be readily compared with their contemporaries. For a precise list of criteria used to calculate each score, click the scorecard version number linked to each device below. For a downloadable (CSV) list of all scores, [click here](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1R_egXm7iwR0isCt_UxcGtheFEwLj9SNhxC5DWnAqKIc/edit=0) .\\n\\n* * *\\n\\n# Laptop Scores\\n\\nSorted by newest to oldest\\n\\n# Lenovo ThinkPad T14 Gen 7 and T16 Gen 5\\n\\n2026\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Storage and memory are readily repairable/upgradeable using industry-standard parts.\\n* The battery is easily replaced, and the keyboard replacement procedure is best-in-class.\\n* Overall very high modularity, including individually replaceable Thunderbolt ports.\\n* Lenovo provides thorough repair instructions and sells replacement parts.\\n\\n[Scorecard v2.2](https://www.ifixit.com/Wiki/Repairability_Scoring_Rubric_v2.2)\\n# MacBook Pro 14-inch (M5, 2025)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/MacBook_Pro_14%22_2025_%28M5%29)\\n\\n2025\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Battery replacements are do-able (if not exactly easy).\\n* The Thunderbolt port design is highly modular and repair-friendly.\\n* Apple offers a full service manual and a good selection of replacement parts for end users.\\n\\n###### CONS\\n\\n* Storage is not removable or serviceable, the keyboard is riveted down, and pentalobe screws bar the way for all repairs.\\n\\n[Scorecard v2.2](https://www.ifixit.com/Wiki/Repairability_Scoring_Rubric_v2.2)\\n\\n# Lenovo ThinkPad P16 Gen 3\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/Lenovo_ThinkPad_P16_Gen_3)\\n\\n2025\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Storage and memory are readily repairable/upgradeable using industry-standard parts.\\n* The battery is easily replaced, and the keyboard replacement procedure is best-in-class.\\n* Lenovo typically provides thorough support for P-series repairs (instructions and replacement parts).\\n\\n###### CONS\\n\\n...\\n\\n# MacBook Air 15″ (M2)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/MacBook_Air_15%22_2023)\\n\\n2023\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Battery repairs are tough but do-able, and the fanless design is low-maintenance.\\n* Apple offers full repair instructions and replacement parts for end users.\\n\\n###### CONS\\n\\n* Storage is soldered, the keyboard is riveted down, and pentalobe screws bar the way for all repairs.\\n\\n[Scorecard v1.6](https://www.ifixit.com/Wiki/Repairability_Scoring_Rubric_v1.6)  \\n**[Learn More](https://www.ifixit.com/News/62674/m2-macbook-air-teardown-apple-forgot-the-heatsink)**\\n\\n# MacBook Air 13″ (M2)\\n\\n[](https://www.ifixit.com/Device/Macbook_Air_M2_2022)\\n\\n2022\\n\\n###### PROS\\n\\n* Battery repairs are tough but do-able, and the fanless design is low-maintenance.\\n* Apple offers full repair instructions and replacement parts for end users.\\n\\n###### CONS\\n\\n* Storage is soldered, the keyboard is riveted down, and pentalobe screws bar the way for all repairs.\\n\\n[Scorecard v1.6](https://www.ifixit.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://support.hp.com/us-en/product/product-specs/omen-by-hp-15-ce000-laptop-pc-series/15551437\",\n      \"title\": \"OMEN by HP 15-ce000 Laptop PC series\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Find full Product Specifications, Accessories and compatibility information for your OMEN by HP 15-ce000 Laptop PC series.\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.blisscomputers.net/hp-omen-15-ce0xx-lcd-screen-15-6-1920x1080-laptop-display-331487\",\n      \"title\": \"description: Low Prices. Fast Shipping. 25 Years in Screen Industry Experience. Buy Online With Confidence! HP omen 15-ce0xx LCD Screen 15.6\\\" 1920x1080 laptop Display. title: HP omen 15-ce0xx LCD Screen 15.6\\\" 1920x1080 laptop Display image: https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-vy9cg/products/566407/images/91347348/11895__13603.1777743224.380.500.jpg?c=2\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"---\\ndescription: Low Prices. Fast Shipping. 25 Years in Screen Industry Experience. Buy Online With Confidence! HP omen 15-ce0xx LCD Screen 15.6&quot; 1920x1080 laptop Display.\\ntitle: HP omen 15-ce0xx LCD Screen 15.6&quot; 1920x1080 laptop Display\\nimage: https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-vy9cg/products/566407/images/91347348/11895__13603.1777743224.380.500.jpg?c=2\\n---\\n\\n <!DOCTYPE html> \\n\\nSearch \\n\\n* [ Home ](https://www.blisscomputers.net/)\\n* [ Non Touch Screen ](https://www.blisscomputers.net/non-touch-screen/)\\n* [ HP omen 15-ce0xx LCD Screen 15.6\\\" 1920x1080 laptop Display ](https://www.blisscomputers.net/hp-omen-15-ce0xx-lcd-screen-15-6-1920x1080-laptop-displ