 for the HP OMEN 15-dc0030nr, a 2018 gaming laptop manufactured by HP.\\n\\nAuthor: Jordan (and 6 other contributors)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\nI Have This\\n\\n## Guides\\n\\n### Replacement Guides\\n\\nThermal Paste Thermal Paste\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### doesnt charge when in use but chargers when not in use\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-dc0030nr |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|3 Answers\\n\\n0 Score |### Spilled water over my laptop / can it be repaired\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-dc0030nr |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Transparent vertical line on screen\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-dc0030nr |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### Where to source good replacement screen?\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-dc0030nr |\\n\\n## [Tools](https://www.ifixit.com/Tools)\\nThese are some common tools used to work on this device. You might not need every tool for every procedure.\\n\\n* [](https://www.ifixit.com/products/phillips-1-screwdriver)\\n  \\n  [Phillips #1 Screwdriver](https://www.ifixit.com/products/phillips-1-screwdriver)\\n  \\n  [View](https://www.ifixit.com/products/phillips-1-screwdriver)\\n* [](https://www.ifixit.com/products/ifixit-thermal-paste)\\n  \\n  [iFixit Thermal Paste](https://www.ifixit.com/products/ifixit-thermal-paste)\\n  \\n  [View](https://www.ifixit.com/products/ifixit-thermal-paste)\\n\\n## Models\\n\\n15-dc0030nr\\n\\n## Background and Identification\\n\\nThe HP OMEN 15-dc0030nr is a gaming laptop, which means it has a powerful processor and is made to support detailed graphics and other high-demand processes that are common in modern games. It is also meant to be easy to upgrade different features, making it more customizable for the user depending on their needs.\\nThis laptop has the diamond-shaped OMEN logo in the bottom center of the screen, and a backlit keyboard. It also has the screen slightly raised from the keyboard by the hinges, which creates a small gap between the two. There are several variations of the HP Omen 15-dc laptop: 15-dc0030 nr, 15-dc0045nr, and 15-dc0051nr.\\n\\n## Technical Specifications\\n\\n* Product number: 3WE66UA\\n* Product name: OMEN by HP - 15-dc0030nr\\n* Dimensions (W x D x H): 36 x 26.3 x 2.6 cm\\n* Weight: 2.52 kg\\n* Operating system: Windows 10 Home 64\\n* Display: 15.6\\\" diagonal FHD IPS anti-glare micro-edge WLED-backlit (1920 x 1080)\\n* Battery type: 4-cell, 70 Wh Li-ion\\n* Power supply type: 200 W AC power adapter\\n* Microprocessor: Intel® Core™ i7-8750H\\n* Memory: 16 GB DDR4-2666 SDRAM (1 x 16 GB)\\n* Webcam: HP Wide Vision HD Camera with integrated dual array digital microphone\\n* Keyboard: Full-size 4-zone lighting backlit keyboard with numeric keypad and NKRO\\n* Audio features: Bang & Olufsen, dual speakers, HP Audio Boost, DTS Headphone:X™ support\\n* Video graphics: NVIDIA® GeForce® GTX 1060 (6 GB GDDR5 dedicated)\\n* Network interface: Integrated 10/100/1000 GbE LAN\\n* Expansion slots: 1 multi-format SD media card reader\\n\\n## Additional Information\\n\\n[HP OMEN 15dc0030nr Review](https://mylaptopguide.com/hp-omen-15-dc0030nr-gaming-laptop-review/)\\n\\n[Full List of Technical Specifications](https://support.hp.com/hk-en/document/c06084808)\\n\\n[Maintenance and Service Guide](http://h10032.www1.hp.com/ctg/Manual/c06219881)\\n\\n### Author\\n\\nwith 6 other contributors\\n\\n#### Jordan\\n\\nMember since: 09/02/18\\n\\n1,159 Reputation\\n\\n4 Guides authored\\n\\nBadges: 13\\n\\n* \\n* \\n* \\n\\n\\\\+10 more badges\\n\\n**View Statistics:**\\n\\nPast 24 Hours: 3\\n\\nPast 7 Days: 42\\n\\nPast 30 Days: 93\\n\\nAll Time: 15,062\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Device/HP_15_Series\",\n      \"title\": \"HP 15 Series Repair Help: Learn How to Fix It Yourself.\",\n      \"publish_date\": null,\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\nHP 15 Series\\n\\nTable of Contents\\n\\n* Background and Identification\\n* Additional Information\\n\\n* Edit\\n* Options\\n\\n* History\\n* \\n* Show Other Languages\\n\\nHP 15 Series\\n\\n# HP 15 Series Repair\\n\\nBudget 15\\\" laptop series released by HP.\\n\\nAuthor: Joseph Sctbunio (and 5 other contributors)\\n\\nCreate a Guide\\n\\n## Popular Forum Questions\\n\\nAsk a Question\\n\\n|3 Answers\\n\\n2 Score |### Laptop won't boot up, power light and charging light flash\\n\\nHP Notebook 15s-fq0000 Series |\\n| --- | --- |\\n|5 Answers\\n\\n9 Score |### My laptop won't turn on\\n\\nHP 15-D076NR |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### What can I upgrade on my laptop?\\n\\nHP 15 Laptop (15-dy) |\\n|1 Answer\\n\\n0 Score |### My computer is black screen and won’t turn on!\\n\\nHP 15-e Series |\\n\\n## Background and Identification\\n\\nThe Hewlett-Packard (HP) Company, now succeeded by HP Inc., is an American multinational information technology (IT) company. HP Inc.\\nis headquartered in Palo Alto, California and primarily develops personal computers and printing related products, including 3D printing. In 2015, the computer and printing departments of the company separated from the rest of the Hewlett-Packard Company to form HP Inc. The Hewlett-Packard Company is now known as the Hewlett Packard Enterprise and oversees the business and enterprise operations of the Hewlett Packard brand.\\n\\nThe ‘15’ in the title refers to the size of the screen of the laptop series. HP laptops can generally be found in the following screen sizes: 13-inch, 15-inch, and 17-inch. As a result, this page will refer to repair documentation and information on HP laptops that include 15-inch sized screens.\\n\\nThe following lines of HP products are or have been produced with a 15-inch (15.6”) screen:\\n\\n* HP 15 Series\\n* HP Envy\\n* HP Pavilion\\n* HP Spectre x360\\n* HP Omen\\n* HP Chromebook\\n* HP EliteBook\\nThis page will cover service and repair information for all models of HP 15 series laptops. The HP 15 Series can be identified by the structure of the following: screen size and model number (ex: 15-ac121dx). The letter after the dash corresponds to various other submodels of the HP 15 Series. Surprisingly, the letters cover almost all letters of the alphabet other than h, i, l, m, o, q, s, t, v, x, y, z.\\n\\n## Additional Information\\n\\n[HP 15 Series Lineup](https://www.notebookcheck.net/HP-15-Series.124890.0.html)\\n\\n[HP Inc. Wikipedia](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HP_Inc.)\\n\\n[Amazon product page](https://www.amazon.com/slp/hp-pavilion-15-notebook-pc/ywrua4dk86g5x6q?tag=ifixitam-20)\\n\\n### Author\\n\\nwith 5 other contributors\\n\\n#### Joseph Sctbunio\\n\\nMember since: 09/23/17\\n\\n7,884 Reputation\\n\\n42 Guides authored\\n\\nBadges: 22\\n\\n* \\n* \\n* \\n\\n\\\\+19 more badges\\n\\n**View Statistics:**\\n\\nPast 24 Hours: 40\\n\\nPast 7 Days: 535\\n\\nPast 30 Days: 1,624\\n\\nAll Time: 107,724\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"url\": \"https://www.ifixit.com/Answers/Device/HP_OMEN_15_Series\",\n      \"title\": \"HP OMEN 15 Series Repair Forum - iFixit\",\n      \"publish_date\": \"2026-06-06\",\n      \"excerpts\": [\n        \"Free Shipping on Domestic Orders $75+\\n\\n# HP OMEN 15 Series Repair Forum\\n\\nAsk\\n\\nLearn How It Works Ask a Question\\n\\nThe only question in the past 3 months has a reply!\\n\\n100%\\n\\nAll Questions\\n\\n* All Questions\\n* Devices\\n* + Members\\n    + Moderation\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\n## **HP OMEN 15 Series** most helpful threads\\n\\nclear\\n\\nMost Helpful\\n\\nAll Most Helpful Unanswered Newest\\n\\nAll Questions\\n\\n* All Questions\\n* Devices\\n* + Members\\n    + Moderation\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx\\n\\n0 Answers\\n\\nHP Omen- No battery detected after replacement\\n\\nunanswered HP Omen 15-ax243dx 0 Answers\\n\\nMahima Singh\\n\\nAnswered\\n\\nMar 15, 2023\\n\\nanswered Mar 15, 2023 by **Mahima Singh**\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx\\n\\n3 Answers\\n\\nHow do I replace the Ram?\\n\\nHP Omen 15-ax243dx 3 Answers\\n\\n[[deleted]](/User/3742465/%5Bdeleted%5D)\\n\\nAnswer edited\\n\\nNov 21, 2020\\n\\nanswer edited Nov 21, 2020 by [**[deleted]**](/User/3742465/%5Bdeleted%5D)\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ax280nd\\n\\n2 Answers\\n\\nWhy won't my hp omen laptop not turn on?\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ax280nd 2 Answers\\n\\nDrue Pautz\\n\\nCommented\\nJun 9, 2024\\n\\ncommented Jun 9, 2024 by **Drue Pautz**\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-dc0030nr\\n\\n2 Answers\\n\\nFull laptop breakdown, including the screen/moniter.\\n\\naccepted HP OMEN 15-dc0030nr 2 Answers\\n\\nAlbert 3\\\\.5k\\n\\nAnswer edited\\n\\nApr 17, 2022\\n\\nanswer edited Apr 17, 2022 by **Albert**\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dh0000 Series\\n\\n1 Answer\\n\\nHP Omen 15-DH0105TX Monitor Glitching Problem\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dh0000 Series 1 Answer\\n\\nDwi Putra 13\\n\\nCommented\\n\\nJun 6, 2026\\n\\ncommented Jun 6, 2026 by **Dwi Putra**\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dc0000 Series\\n\\n1 Answer\\n\\nMy laptop heats up\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dc0000 Series 1 Answer\\n\\noldturkey03 858\\\\.9k\\n\\nAnswered\\n\\nFeb 16, 2026\\n\\nanswered Feb 16, 2026 by **oldturkey03**\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series\\n\\n1 Answer\\n\\nNo image after replacing thermal paste\\n\\nHP OMEN 15 Series 1 Answer\\n\\nSebastian 13\\n\\nCommented\\n\\nSep 15, 2024\\n\\ncommented Sep 15, 2024 by **Sebastian**\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ek0000 Series\\n\\n1 Answer\\n\\nHow to enable Advance bios in HP Omen 15 (2020)\\n\\nHP OMEN 15-ek0000 Series 1 Answer\\n\\nNickolas Delgado 602\\n\\nAnswered\\n\\nJul 18, 2023\\nanswered Jul 18, 2023 by **Nickolas Delgado**\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dc0000 Series\\n\\n1 Answer\\n\\nkeys (especially around wasd) dont work after replacing the battery\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dc0000 Series 1 Answer\\n\\nJacob Mehnert 49k\\n\\nAnswered\\n\\nJun 9, 2023\\n\\nanswered Jun 9, 2023 by **Jacob Mehnert**\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dc0000 Series\\n\\n1 Answer\\n\\nDoes the motherboard turn on by itself?\\n\\naccepted HP Omen 15-dc0000 Series 1 Answer\\n\\npaydownant 23\\n\\nAccepted an answer\\n\\nJun 7, 2023\\n\\nanswer accepted Jun 7, 2023 by **paydownant**\\n\\nHP Omen 15-dc0000 Series\\n\\n1 Answer\\n\\nOpened my laptop up to repaste, now no display (water)\\