      "text": "I found that the HP Omen 15-ax243dx has a repairability score of 7/10. However, the user's model is HP OMEN 15-ce0xx, which might be similar but not exactly the same. I should check if there's a specific iFixit page for HP OMEN 15-ce0xx. Let me search for \"HP OMEN 15-ce0xx iFixit\" more specifically.",
